flavor: If the Indomidible Error has entered your path, even the greatest of warriors would hazard you.
Wizards of the Crystal peaks magic council have fled it's wrath.
Thieves and their ilk, who lust for gold, have taken costly measures to avoid it's gaze.
The world shakes and shivers from it's influence, as even painters prefer colors that are less similar to it's glow.
Run, dear friends. Run and hide.
kill: The Error does not die. It merely hides until the next mistake.